{"tid":872272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GOT7王嘉爾:「他是最了解我的人」","createTime":"2018-10-22T14:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:25:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58f49cf6d5e0aeda8a33fd9c76f210a8ceca79ba","tid":872272,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"GOT7王嘉爾簽約陳澤杉！　「他是最了解我的人」<br />\n<br />\n「先鋒音樂人」王嘉爾將攜手素有「巨星推手」之稱的陳澤杉並聯合燦星製作，共同在北京萬國體育國際擊劍奧體中心召開新聞發佈會，三方強強聯手，共同開創國際音樂舞台，王嘉爾也拋出震撼彈，「我跟杉哥的關係與合作是沒有時間限制的。」<br />\n<br />\n作為一名全能藝人，更是流行音樂先鋒唱作人，王嘉爾的音樂理念和創作風格一直是樂壇獨樹一幟的存在。從2017-2018，王嘉爾的四首單曲一經發行便席捲各大榜單。<span style=\"color: red;\">單曲《PAPILLON》MV發佈第二周，YouTube播放量即正式突破千萬，創下華語樂壇新紀錄；隨後《Dawn of us》則迅速拿下新浪微博亞洲新曲榜第一名；《Fendiman》更使王嘉爾成為第一位獲得ITunes美區單曲總榜及流行榜雙榜冠軍的中國歌手。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3639/d3639988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3639%2Fd3639988.jpg&h=a57a1166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼王嘉爾和陳澤杉簽約合作。（圖／燦星文化提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3639/d3639987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3639%2Fd3639987.jpg&h=7c5a03ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，<span style=\"color: red;\">2018年王嘉爾還成為首位獲得Teen Choice Awards（全美青少年頒獎典禮）明日之星獎的華人，他的IG追蹤人數亦是全華人之最，粉絲數高達1133萬，王嘉爾憑藉個人魅力和過硬實力，90後的他早已在各個領域落下濃墨重彩。他是音樂尖端的潮流先鋒，也是全力以赴的逐夢青年。</span><br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，陳澤杉也在今天實現諾言，加入燦星文化後，第一位點名合作的藝人就是王嘉爾，陳澤杉表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">「王嘉爾是目前新生代中極少數能夠進軍國際的藝人，我和他的共同點就是希望能夠一起攜手進軍國際舞台發展。」</span><br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾則說：「我選擇和杉哥合作是因為他在這麼多人當中，是最了解我要什麼的人，還有知道我所追求的夢想，了解我最適合什麼，未來的演藝之路怎麼規劃，所以我非常幸運可以跟杉哥合作，我跟杉哥的關係與合作是沒有時間限制的。」"},{"pid":"e1f4443d18ecbc2d5560b931af2ab56d7dc5f3a4","tid":872272,"uid":52073,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"收聲啦"},{"pid":"5a31fbae92394d2889fcaa7b95042e539deb1930","tid":872272,"uid":193951,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"支持嘎嘎衝出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5912a8235368abb372fd11db314975310a463b7a","tid":872272,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f4443d18ecbc2d5560b931af2ab56d7dc5f3a4","tid":872272,"uid":52073,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"收聲啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"lan la傻鳩"},{"pid":"dda72fa03174fa1b390942498bc586c65ccea309","tid":872272,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5912a8235368abb372fd11db314975310a463b7a","tid":872272,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f4443d18ecbc2d5560b931af2ab56d7dc5f3a4","tid":872272,"uid":52073,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"收聲啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"lan la傻鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"反嘎嘎咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a02efa33d671a712ce2f6339d82c38355308a0","tid":872272,"uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"嘉爾BB真係香港之光 中國之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c9793ba3c95c5aaa11fc746b9430fc49b24c5b","tid":872272,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"娘炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dab645584b6d2817ae764e75fb372e1b58699e8","tid":872272,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dda72fa03174fa1b390942498bc586c65ccea309","tid":872272,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5912a8235368abb372fd11db314975310a463b7a","tid":872272,"uid":193951,"lik